OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,FThe Bristol Beacon refurbishment
OL,8,Factually cost taxpayers #183m, a
OL,9,Fcouncillor has claimed.
OL,11,FThe Bristol Beacon, an historic music
OL,12,Fhall, went through a five-year
OL,13,Frenovation ending in November 2023
OL,14,Fwhen it reopened to visitors.
OL,16,FOriginally it was thought the total
OL,17,Fcost came to #132m - almost three
OL,18,Ftimes the original #48m budget.
