OL,5,Ccouncillor
OL,7,FAt the time of reopening, the chief
OL,8,FExecutive of Bristol Beacon said the
OL,9,Fbuilding was "in a worse state than
OL,10,Fanybody could have imagined" when the
OL,11,Fproject began.
OL,13,FWith the #132m figure total, it was
OL,14,Fbelieved #84.5m was paid for by the
OL,15,Fowners - Bristol City Council.
OL,17,FTo fund that, the authority is having
OL,18,Fto take out a series of loans over the
OL,19,Fnext 50 years, with annual repayments
OL,20,Fof #2.2m a year.
