OL,7,FMr Young accepted in an email to the
OL,8,FCllr Hucker that longer-term borrowing
OL,9,Fcould level out at 3.25% interest
OL,10,Fduring the term of the loans, which
OL,11,Fwould amount to #157million.
OL,13,FCllr Hucker pointed out the 50-year
OL,14,Floan rate from the Public Works Loan
OL,15,FBoard (PWLB), which councils borrow
OL,16,Fmoney from, was currently more than 5%.
OL,18,FCllr Hucker said even the total bill
OL,19,Fhe expected of #183million was
OL,20,F"optimistic".
