OL,7,FThe council said that since it started
OL,8,Fpaying for the refurbishment in 2016,
OL,9,Fit had borrowed #345million to fund
OL,10,Fall of its major capital projects, not
OL,11,Fjust the Beacon. It said it's done
OL,12,Fthis mostly by using its own cash at
OL,13,Fan average interest rate of 1.25%.
OL,15,FDuring that time, it borrowed
OL,16,F#49.2million externally long-term at
OL,17,Fan average interest rate of 1.93% and
OL,18,Fthen a further #50million on a one-
OL,19,Fyear deal with 5.43% interest.
